languages.text: "А что поменялось? Как были под железной пятой, так и остались. Разве что теперь не на площади жгут, а по-тихому пулю в затылок пускают или в сервиторы отдают..."

"But what's changed? How's one iron fist different from another? I suppose you might say they don't burn people in the square anymore. Now they put a discreet bullet in the back of your head, or else they give you to the servitors..."

languages.text: “可这又有什么不一样呢？反正都是铁腕统治，谁的铁腕有区别吗？我猜你可以说，他们现在不会在广场上把人活活烧死了。他们现在只会偷偷摸摸地朝你后脑勺开枪，或者把你交给那群机仆……”
languages.original_text: "But what's changed? How's one iron fist different from another? I suppose you might say they don't burn people in the square anymore. Now they put a discreet bullet in the back of your head, or else they give you to the servitors..."

languages.text: 「でも、何が変わったって言う？鉄拳であるのに変わりはないだろう？確かに、広場で人が焼かれることはなくなったかもしれない。でも、今の彼らはコッソリと人の後頭部を撃つ。さもなければ、サーヴィターに連れていかせる」

languages.text: «Pero, ¿qué ha cambiado? ¿En qué se diferencia un puño de hierro de otro? Supongo que se podría decir que ya no queman a la gente en la plaza. Ahora te meten una bala en la nuca discretamente o te entregan a los servidores...».
languages.original_text: "But what's changed? How's one iron fist different from another? I suppose you might say they don't burn people in the square anymore. Now they put a discreet bullet in the back of your head, or else they give you to the servitors..."

languages.text: "Aber was hat sich verändert? Was unterscheidet die eine eiserne Faust von der anderen? Gut, man könnte sagen, dass sie niemanden mehr auf dem Platz verbrennen. Sie verpassen einem jetzt eine diskrete Kugel in den Hinterkopf oder händigen einen den Servitoren aus ..."

languages.text: « Mais qu'est-ce qui a changé, finalement ? En quoi la poigne de fer de l'un est-elle différente de celle d'un autre ? Certes, ils ne brûlent plus les gens sur la place publique, mais maintenant, à la place, ils vous tirent une balle dans la tête ou, pire encore, ils vous confient aux bons soins des servitors... »

languages.text: "Fakat değişen ne? Bir demir yumruğu diğerinden farklı kılan ne? Artık insanları meydanda yakmıyorlar. Onun yerine kafanın ardına kurşunu gizlice sokuveriyor veya hizmetörlere veriveriyorlar."

traits.locale_text: "Ama değişen ne? Bir demir yumruğu diğerinden farklı kılan ne? Sanırım artık insanları meydanda yakmadıkları söylenebilir. Onun yerine kafanın arkasına kurşunu gizlice sokuveriyorlar veya seni hizmetörlere veriveriyorlar."
